Leading Pharmacist and former Board member of Diabetes NSW & ACT, John Bell
AM, is honoured with the 2019 Sir Kempson Maddox Award
### Leo Tutt, awarded Member of the Order of Australia
Diabetes NSW & ACT Chairman, Leo Tutt has been awarded the Member of the Order
of Australia in the 2018 Queens Birthday Honours.
